00:01:30.350 --> 00:01:34.940
Episode 15: Justice Part 2

00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:35.500
Polnareff... I want to kill you!

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:40.210
I want to avenge my son
by ripping out your insides!

